reviewText: My kids love Little People. Well done pre-computer Claymation. If you're sick of all these computer-generated kids shows, try this one.
Granddaughter loves this. Keeps her entertained while I am cooking.
Bought this for my youngest since my older two loved these.

My 15 month LOVES these videos.....he will watch them over and over again! The only problem I have is that the song is very catchy and I will find myself singing to it throughout the day, even when we're not watching it :)
Again, the little ones like these dvd's
If your little one likes the "Little people  series" this is well worth the money. The two disc set will keep them glued to the set for a while watching appropriate entertainment for little ones.
My 4 year old daughter LOVES Little People
